@piquark6046
If adshield fails to block ads on protected websites, shouldn't Adguard handle the exception? Adguard will try to force a block, causing it to crash and ultimately ruining the user experience.

It is better to see advertisements than to have a broken website. So please handle the exception so that users don't experience this problem.

